em. after the upgrade to owncloud 5.0.7, the webinterface itself works fine but i witnessed a memory exhaustion problem while trying to use webdav:\r\n\r\n<snip>\r\n[21-jun-2013 10:58:14 utc] php fatal error:  allowed memory size of 134217728 bytes exhausted (tried to allocate 523800 bytes) in /srv/www/oc.fumarmata.net/apps/user_ldap/lib/connection.php on line 596\r\n</snip>\r\n\r\ni experimented with the memory_limit variable in my php.ini, setting it from 128m to 254m and 512m to no avail. i then took the risk and set it to -1 and as soon as i tried to login into webdav, php-fpm started to eat all available memory and the system essentially came to a halt.\r\n\r\ni am using fedora/389 as directory server.\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"mattiasgiese","id":2472944,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/6db087d16a1a5574c0a11ad8253e62ef?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fd65e58fe374f9a7497adbecc78aa6f56.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"6db087d16a1a5574c0a11ad8253e62ef","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese","html_url":"https://github.com/mattiasgiese","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mattiasgiese/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}